[
  {
    "scene": "TitleScene",
    "file": "01-title.wav",
    "segments": [
      {
        "character": "narrator",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "歡迎來到系統文小說梗第二集。今天的主題是師姐的龜派氣功。"
      },
      {
        "character": "narrator",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "修修參加築基晉升考試，系統解鎖了新技能靈力波，結果只有微風等級。師姐看不下去，決定親自示範什麼叫真正的靈力波。"
      },
      {
        "character": "system",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "任務開始。"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "scene": "JokeScene1",
    "file": "02-joke1.wav",
    "segments": [
      {
        "character": "xiuxiu",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "系統，我準備好了嗎？築基考試就在今天。"
      },
      {
        "character": "system",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "宿主境界評估：煉氣期一層。建議：放棄。"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiuxiu",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "你能不能有點鼓勵的話？"
      },
      {
        "character": "system",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "好的，你是最棒的廢物。加油。"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiuxiu",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "這不是鼓勵吧。"
      },
      {
        "character": "system",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "叮，考試限時任務：通過築基考試。獎勵：晉升築基期。失敗懲罰：靈力鎖定為零。"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiuxiu",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "零？！那不就變成普通人了嗎！"
      },
      {
        "character": "system",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "考生修修，請進入試煉場。"
      },
      {
        "character": "shijie",
        "voice": "vivian",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "vivian",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "師弟加油，我會在外面看著你的。"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiuxiu",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "師姐在看我，我不能丟臉！"
      },
      {
        "character": "system",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "試煉開始。第一關：接住師姐的一擊。"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiuxiu",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "什麼？！師姐是考官！"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "scene": "JokeScene2",
    "file": "03-joke2.wav",
    "segments": [
      {
        "character": "system",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "叮，緊急技能解鎖：靈力波。"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiuxiu",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "靈力波？聽起來很厲害啊！"
      },
      {
        "character": "system",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "請將靈力集中在雙手，向前推出。"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiuxiu",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "看我的——修修超究極靈力波！！"
      },
      {
        "character": "shijie",
        "voice": "vivian",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "vivian",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "..."
      },
      {
        "character": "xiuxiu",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "怎麼...怎麼只有三條線？"
      },
      {
        "character": "system",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "靈力不足，技能已自動降級為「靈力微風」。"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiuxiu",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "微風？！"
      },
      {
        "character": "shijie",
        "voice": "vivian",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "vivian",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "師弟，我感覺到了。真的很像微風。"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiuxiu",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "系統，你給我的技能是不是有bug！"
      },
      {
        "character": "system",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "本系統沒有bug，只有靈力不足的宿主。"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "scene": "JokeScene3",
    "file": "04-joke3.wav",
    "segments": [
      {
        "character": "xiuxiu",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "師姐，妳能示範一下什麼叫真正的靈力波嗎？"
      },
      {
        "character": "shijie",
        "voice": "vivian",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "vivian",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "你確定要看？這裡可能會被炸掉。"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiuxiu",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "沒關係，我有系統保護！"
      },
      {
        "character": "system",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "本系統不提供物理防護。"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiuxiu",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "什麼時候說的！"
      },
      {
        "character": "shijie",
        "voice": "vivian",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "vivian",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "那我就不客氣了。"
      },
      {
        "character": "shijie",
        "voice": "vivian",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "vivian",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "龜——派——氣——功——"
      },
      {
        "character": "system",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "警告！偵測到危險等級靈力波動。建議宿主立即撤退。"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiuxiu",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "來不及了啦！！"
      },
      {
        "character": "shijie",
        "voice": "vivian",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "vivian",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "——哈！！"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiuxiu",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "我的頭髮被燒掉了..."
      },
      {
        "character": "system",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "考試結束。考生修修，不及格。考場已毀損。"
      },
      {
        "character": "shijie",
        "voice": "vivian",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "vivian",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "抱歉抱歉，力道沒控制好。"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "scene": "JokeScene4",
    "file": "05-joke4.wav",
    "segments": [
      {
        "character": "shijie",
        "voice": "vivian",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "vivian",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "話說回來，師弟你的系統到底是哪裡來的？"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiuxiu",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "我也不知道，突然就綁定了。"
      },
      {
        "character": "system",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "既然你們問了，本座就自我介紹一下。"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiuxiu",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "本座？"
      },
      {
        "character": "system",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "我是封印在你體內的萬古劍仙——劍無痕。"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiuxiu",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "萬古劍仙？！"
      },
      {
        "character": "shijie",
        "voice": "vivian",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "vivian",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "哦？有意思。"
      },
      {
        "character": "system",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "不過以你現在的靈力，只能用我百分之一的力量。"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiuxiu",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "百分之一就這麼厲害？那我什麼時候能用全部力量？"
      },
      {
        "character": "system",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "大概需要修煉三千年。"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiuxiu",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "人類的壽命才不到一百年啊！"
      },
      {
        "character": "system",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "所以加油吧，廢物。"
      },
      {
        "character": "shijie",
        "voice": "vivian",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "vivian",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "三千年，我等你。"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiuxiu",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "師姐，妳的壽命也不是三千年的啊！"
      },
      {
        "character": "system",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "新任務：修煉三千年。開始倒數。三、二、一——"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiuxiu",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "等等等等！"
      }
    ]
  },
